delta lambda scenario timestep i[ind]=
	delta perc lambda scenario timestep i[ind]*lambda policy start i[ind]
	~	Euro constant/(Hours*Person)
	~	Relative change in current timestep in productivity in each sector respect \
		to S Time policy start when Act change labour productivity !=0
	|

delta NFI consumption impact=
	0.1
	~	
	~		|

