max capacity factor[e nec]=
	RES transition*
	(IF THEN ELSE(Time>=S Time Policy start,
	init max cf nec+
	(final max cf nec-init max cf nec)/
	(1+EXP(-steepness logistic curve*(Time-midpoint logistic curve
	))),
	init max cf nec))
	
	+(1-RES transition)*
	(init max cf nec)
	~	Dmnl
	~	Maximum capacity factor for non-RES from Jaxa-Rozen et al., 2022; for RES we assume \
		priority of dispatch and hence that the actual capacity factor is equal to \
		the maximum capacity factor.
		Due to the change of mix bewtween bio and geothermal in nec, the value for \
		nec is dynamic. For simplicity we again assume a liner extrapolation over \
		time.
	|

