[gini6]+pop share ordered gini[gini7]+pop share ordered gini[gini8]+pop share ordered gini
[gini9]+pop share ordered gini[gini10]+pop share ordered gini[gini11]+pop share ordered gini
[gini12]+pop share ordered gini[gini13]+pop share ordered gini[gini14]+pop share ordered gini
[gini15]<0.4, gini16,
